history.content:
I have not taken stat140, taking stat134 now. If you've been following this page, you already know you are advised to take ee126 after taking cs70. I think stat140 starts off faster and is in general harder than 134.

-------

Stat 140 is harder than 134 but easier than ee126. If you found CS70's probability section challenging, you can probably take stat140. If you found probability section easy/manageable, you can take ee126. I don't think stat134 is worth taking after cs70. You can take either stat140 or ee126.

Also, how does it compare to STAT 134?

Thanks in advance!
